Owncast is a self-hosted live video and web chat server for use with
existing popular broadcasting software. Point your live stream at a
server you personally control and regain ownership over your content.

Owncast is a single service that you can run that works out of the box,
streaming from multimedia/obs-studio, or multimedia/vlc, and many other
similar projects, and allows you to live stream to your participants,
with a lightweight chat interface.

WWW: https://owncast.online/
